text: Winston Hills is an electoral district of New South Wales. It was created in 2023, mostly replacing the abolished electorate of Seven Hills. It is a conservative electorate that has only ever been held by the Liberal Party. Winston Hills in the Hills District of Sydney, which is the most conservative (Liberal-leaning) district of any Australian capital city. However, it is the least conservative electorate in the Hills District. ==Election results== ==References== Category:2023 establishments in Australia Winston Hills
